      "tag": "flaw",
      "extra": "He is named after a group of gaijin visitors who were greatly impressed by the lands of Rokugan and its history. They were suspected of assisting in the kidnapping of Kitsuni Amake, JohnDavid's mother. They, in fact, were instrumental in helping Hideki, JohnDavid's father, recover Amake from her actual kidnappers. "
